org.apache.lucene.spatial.prefix.AbstractVisitingPrefixTreeQuery
org.apache.lucene.spatial.prefix.IntersectsPrefixTreeQuery
public class IntersectsPrefixTreeQuery extends AbstractVisitingPrefixTreeQuery
A Query matching documents that have an SpatialRelation.INTERSECTS (i.e. not DISTINCT) relationship with a provided query shape.
NOTE: This API is for internal purposes only and might change in incompatible ways in the next release.
